\n---\n```\n\n## 记录要求\n\n1. 写入文件：`memory/人体进化思考日志.md`\n2. 追加格式，保留历史\n3. 每次思考 300-500 字\n4. 基于真实科学研究\n\n开始第 1 次思考！"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce"},"state":{"lastRunAtMs":1774316769364,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":72735,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"nextRunAtMs":1774318200000,"lastDelivered":true}},{"id":"20ad25e9-a93b-4554-9c04-ac4c8f1f3016","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"飞书备份方案持续研究","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774139057733,"updatedAtMs":1774317034593,"schedule":{"expr":"15,45 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请研究飞书多维表格（Bitable）备份方案的可行性：\n\n## 研究任务\n\n1. **分析失败原因**\n   - 检查 feishu_bitable_create_app API 调用参数\n   - 尝试不同的参数组合（folder_token、name 等）\n   - 记录具体错误信息\n\n2. **替代方案探索**\n   - 方案 A：云文档 + 表格块（用 feishu_doc create_table）\n   - 方案 B：使用现有 Bitable（如果用户已有）\n   - 方案 C：云盘文件备份（JSON 原始数据）\n\n3. **实践测试**\n   - 尝试用 feishu_doc 在文档中创建表格\n   - 测试表格内容写入\n   - 验证是否可实现类似 Bitable 的结构化存储\n\n4. **输出报告**\n   - 哪种方案最可行？\n   - 需要什么额外权限？\n   - 推荐什么备份策略？\n\n## 记录要求\n\n写入文件：`memory/飞书备份研究日志.md`\n- 研究时间\n- 尝试的方法\n- 成功/失败\n- 下一步计划\n\n记住：目标是找到可靠的飞书备份方案，不一定要用 Bitable！"},"delivery":{"channel":"feishu","mode":"announce","to":"user:ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1"},"state":{"lastRunAtMs":1774316842099,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":192494,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"nextRunAtMs":1774318500000}},{"id":"0e8e73f3-a229-41cd-86fd-b82d7056a8b6","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"GitHub 自动备份推送","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774059323972,"updatedAtMs":1774312642856,"schedule":{"expr":"0 0,6,12,18 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行 GitHub 备份推送：\n\ncd C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"自动备份推送\" || ech